content:
I am Yingjing Huang (Ivy Wong), a M.S student in Geographic Information Science (GIS) at the School of Resource and Environmental Sciences , Wuhan University, supervised by Dr. Teng Fei. I got bachelor’s degree from the Department of Geographic Science, School of Resource and Environmental Sciences , Wuhan University.
Meanwhile, I write some code out of interest including machine learning, front end, and so on. More info can be found in my GitHub.
